OL,7,FThe seven gang members will all be
OL,8,Fmonitored for life after being
OL,9,Fconvicted of gang raping a child and
OL,10,Fabusing other children in a drugs den
OL,11,Fwhere heroin and crack cocaine were
OL,12,Fused.
OL,14,FIain Owens, 46; Elaine Lannery, 40;
OL,15,FLesley Williams, 43; Paul Brannan, 42;
OL,16,FScott Forbes, 51; Barry Watson, 48;
OL,17,Fand John Clark, 48, were convicted in
OL,18,FNovember 2023 following a trial at the
OL,19,FHigh Court in Glasgow.
